at|mitche:  Marty Bergen invented something for this situation: 
I think you'll find it in Bergen's  "bid better play better" book.
         1@s - X - 2@s  shows a weak raise with 3-card support.
Bergen suggests that 2@c in this auction -
         1@S - X - 2@c   shows 7-9 HCP and 3-card support.
And also - 
         1@S - X - 2@d    shows 7-9 HCP and 4-card support.|
